1.1.name: wordpress/rolas-sepuluh
1.1.description: Free Wordpress theme with black and white color. Made by using Blueprint CSS Framework. With custom header, custom background and also supporting thumbnails and drop down menus. Sidebar widgets with three different size. Archives page template, and image attachment page available.
